### 1. Login para obtener Token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_user",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Guardar el token de la respuesta
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 2. Crear un Post (Requiere Auth)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Mi primer post",
  "content": "Contenido del post persistido en JSON"
}

### 3. Obtener Estad√≠sticas (Requiere Admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/posts/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Crear un Comentario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/posts/ID_DEL_POST/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Excelente aporte"
}